    "body": "## Tool/Integration Suggestion\n\n**BuyWhere MCP** — Real-time Singapore product catalog for AI agents\n\nFor developers building AutoGen agents that need to handle Southeast Asia shopping queries, BuyWhere provides:\n\n- Live product pricing across Harvey Norman, Shopee, Lazada (Singapore)\n- 1,000+ products, updated daily\n- MCP-native: single tool call returns structured results\n- No scraping, no rate limits\n\n**Example use case:**\nAn AutoGen shopping research agent that answers \"What'\\''s the cheapest laptop under 000 in Singapore?\" can call BuyWhere to get live, structured data from 3+ platforms.\n\n**Links:**\n- GitHub: https://github.com/BuyWhere/buywhere-mcp\n- Docs: https://buywhere.ai/developers/\n\nHappy to provide integration examples if useful.",
